name: Name
creator: Creator

edit section description: <0/> modifies section <1>{{ sectionId }}</1> of subspace <2>{{ subspaceId }}</2>

delete user group description: <0/> deletes user group <1>{{ groupId }}</1> from subspace <2>{{ subspaceId }}</2>
